  "name": "Greater Shield Specialization",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/weapon_14.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Your masterful shieldwork provides even greater protection to your vital areas.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Proficiency with selected shield, Greater Shield Focus, Shield Focus, Shield Specialization with selected shield, fighter level 12th.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>Choose one type of shield (buckler, light, heavy, or tower shield) for which you possess the Shield Specialization feat. With the selected shield, you gain a +2 bonus to your Armor Class against critical hit confirmation rolls (this bonus stacks with that from Shield Specialization). In addition, once per day you may negate a critical hit, and damage is instead rolled normally.<br/><br/><b>Special</b><br/>You can gain this feat multiple times. Its effects do not stack. Each time you take the feat, it applies to a new type of shield.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>You can spend 5 stamina points to use your selected shield to negate a critical hit a second time each day.",
